window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Climb the Isles. Build his team. Become the champion.</b></p> <p>When a bridge collapses, Ryan should have died. Instead, his stubborn struggles to refuse death are noticed, and he is saved. A wise, very old man transports him to a strange magical realm, filled with floating islands, deadly battles, sinister puzzles, and unique challenges. Not everything is dire, as the climb to become a champion generates opportunities, and a few lovely new allies. Joined by Companions brought forth to aid his quest, Ryan must ascend to the peak to claim his place as a true Champion, and maybe have a little fun along the way.</p> <p>Warning: This book contains untraditional relationships.</p>"; 
